{"tid":278183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明睇NBA既人係咩心態","createTime":"2017-06-10T08:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T13:12:43.000Z","uid":5549,"like":49,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4390341d0ed5f052b0403b27b5ccda6862bcce3","tid":278183,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"先唔講nba d人體能有幾差 個個咁大隻打幾分鐘又要換人同埋係冷氣房打波呢d係人都鬧既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\nnba個垃圾賽制不設降班 包尾個隊仲要有選秀權 即係鼓勵d起步脫晒腳爭唔到季後賽既球隊繼續輸波攬住個包尾位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD常規賽打咁耐其實係冇意思 只係用黎7盤4勝可以打多個主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住D波10場有9場係睇最後個1分鐘就得 <br />\n一場仲要幾百個停頓位 緊張關頭就timeout去廣告 <br />\n<br />\n咁既運動都日日走去追既人究竟係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf6f7adb9e06b8396e9864e5e63e3a5a5d7b5da","tid":278183,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4391ed9dfe2072be1a8d8caae9c2d0cf62729810","tid":278183,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8e9964f31273e589e74aacbdab185f87f321d23","tid":278183,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750f7d317d57f9c669592d6b6c661c89c90e5bdc","tid":278183,"uid":43897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:59:20.000Z","msg":"玩玩具"},{"pid":"ad58b6432ff2876851473a1cb848a7bfcffa9a93","tid":278183,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"樓豬左右不分"},{"pid":"e248c3910b2c69252519bd2826fad78b1a167bbe","tid":278183,"uid"